0.01 2025-12-06
  - Add AWS Signature Version 4 signing to Mojo::UserAgent
  - Support for AWS services (S3, DynamoDB, SQS, SNS, Lambda, etc.)
  - Signed and unsigned payload options
  - Session token support for temporary credentials
  - Custom region and service endpoint configuration
  - Debug mode for signature troubleshooting
  - Configurable request expiration
  - File-based payload support for large uploads
  - Comprehensive test suite with near-100% coverage
  - Full POD documentation